quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  84,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  84,1,jab aasman phatt jaye ga
  84,2,aur apne perwar-digaar ka farmaan baja laaye ga aur usay wajib bhi yeh hi hai
  84,3,aur jab zameen hamwar kar di jaye gi
  84,4,jo kuch is mein hai usay nikaal kar bahar daal day gi aur ( bilkul ) khaali ho jaye gi
  84,5,aur apne perwar-digaar ke irshad ki tameel kere gi aur is ko lazim bhi yahi hai ( to qayamat qaim ho jaye gi )
  84,6,ae ensaan! to apne perwar-digaar ki taraf ( pounchanay mein ) khoob koshish karta hai so is se ja miley ga
  84,7,to jis ka namaa ٴ ( aamaal ) is ke dahinay haath mein diya jaye ga
  84,8,is se hisaab aasaan liya jaye ga
  84,9,aur woh apne ghar walon mein khush khush aeye ga
  84,10,aur jis ka namaaٴ ( aamaal ) is ki peeth ke peechay se diya jaye ga
  84,11,woh mout ko pukare ga
  84,12,aur woh dozakh mein daakhil ho ga
  84,13,yeh apne ahal ( o Ayal ) mein mast rehta tha
  84,14,aur khayaal karta tha ke ( khuda ki taraf ) phir kar nah jaye ga
  84,15,haan haan. is ka perwar-digaar is ko dekh raha tha
  84,16,hamein shaam ki surkhi ki qasam
  84,17,aur raat ki aur jin cheezon ko woh akhatta kar layte hai un ki
  84,18,aur chaand ki jab kaamil ho jaye
  84,19,ke tum darja badarja (rutba ٴ aala par ) charho ge
  84,20,to un logon kokiya howa hai ke imaan nahi laatay
  84,21,aur jab un ke samnay quran parha jata hai to sajda nahi karte
  84,22,balkay kafir jutlatay hain
  84,23,aur khuda un baton ko jo yeh apne dilon mein chupatay hain khoob jaanta hai
  84,24,to un ko dukh dainay walay azaab ki khabar suna do
  84,25,haan jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un ke liye be intahaa ajar hai
